.DT
su
Discworld player help
su

Name
.SI 5
su - switch user.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
su <name>
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
Su stands for switch user.  It will let you log in as a different person without
actually quitting from the mud and logging in again.  Effectively it will quit
you and then start logging you in as the name you specify.  It will then ask
for a password.  You can then just log in as normal.  For creators,
when you log in as your name, you are a player.  When you log in with a :
in front of your name, you are a creator.
.EP

Examples :
.SI 5
> su furball
> su pinkfish
> su tokzic
> su frog
> su :frog
.EI

See also
.SI 5
quit
.EI
